{"tid":1955984,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「修行」塔羅占卜","createTime":"2020-04-03T00:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T21:14:15.000Z","uid":11664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"89eea3c7a541681f57a0eabf0ffc7870d1fd0d5b","tid":1955984,"uid":11664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:49:13.000Z","msg":"直覺塔羅修行中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n免費幫巴絲塔羅占卜 當然就唔包準啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想試試嘅可以Add tg問：<a href=\"https://t.me/tarotthefool\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftarotthefool&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMk9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=f4856909\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tarotthefool</a><br />\n<br />\n稱呼（關於對象就最好有埋啦）<br />\n性別<br />\n你嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n需要準確嘅問題 例如：同個女仔有冇機會？個男仔對我嘅意思係？有冇機會複合？etc<br />\n<br />\n每人限問一條 當然會盡量答哂你想問嘅嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n時間係大約一個月內發生嘅事<br />\n資料方面你想俾幾多就幾多 當然越詳盡準成度越高啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係唔占嘅問題 例如：幾時出Pool 幾時發達 有冇人鐘意你 幾時會有人鐘意你 真命天子出現咗未etc<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係全職占卜 所以可能會應得慢啲 各位體諒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家要以禮相待呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安"},{"pid":"650c36f90f70bd157a95e08d09236bb6ec099567","tid":1955984,"uid":11664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:53:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"728f358fb18ccf3f437d4522586e5d0fa8c9bb18","tid":1955984,"uid":113189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:57:32.000Z","msg":"稱呼wing<br />\n性別 女<br />\n你嘅問題 想知對象點睇我 會唔會有發展機會<br />\n<br />\n感謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b576fbe53b0ffa65b72a34e5fe59ea0743ec8928","tid":1955984,"u